OL,5, A water company that has imposed a     
OL,6, hosepipe ban has blamed people working 
OL,7, from home for the shortage.            
OL,9,FSouth East Water, which supplies more  
OL,10,Fthan two million homes and businesses  
OL,11,Fin Sussex and Kent, will implement the 
OL,12,Frestriction from Monday.               
OL,14,FChief Executive David Hinton said      
OL,15,Fdemand had swelled by about 20% over a 
OL,16,Fshort period of time which had put the 
OL,17,Fexisting infrastructure under stress.  
OL,19,FCustomers said the real problem was the
OL,20,Fcompany's lack of investment.          
